Output diskdoc.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1100
Set Height 720
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 0.5
Set Padding 20

Hide
Type "rm -f /tmp/.diskdoc-mock-scanned && clear"
Enter
Show

Sleep 1500ms
Type "./bin/diskdoc --scan"
Sleep 1000ms
Enter
Sleep 18s

Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 800ms

Type "./bin/diskdoc"
Sleep 1000ms
Enter
Sleep 35s
